{"tid":525010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【再揭虐兒案】3歲女被獨留家老師報警 母發難咬傷2警","createTime":"2018-01-10T07:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T08:00:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2efead6daeb4b346dc62fde5829eae889e9be96f","tid":525010,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180110/large/1515570068_bcbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180110%2Flarge%2F1515570068_bcbf.jpg&h=1b57d14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5歲女童臨臨被父母虐殺一案，有專家質疑校方對受害女童情況未有提高警覺。長沙灣蘇屋邨牡丹樓，早上11時半，有幼稚園老師報警，指其校一名年僅3歲女生報稱「自己一個人在家」，老師擔心女童安全，立即報警求助。警員及消防員接報趕往單位，發現女童獨留在家，消防正要爆門之際，此時女童母親返回，惟看見警員在場，情緒激動，發難咬傷其中2名警員，女童母稍後被制服，涉嫌虐兒及襲警，她雙手反鎖被捕帶署，而女童則在社工陪同下送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鄰居曾投訴女童家不時發出噪音，現場消息指，3、4個月前女童母親不准女兒返學及將她獨留在家，情況與今日如出一徹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180110/57689059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F57689059&d=0F%2F3G%2BKy%2F4cf3VPMUpUJ2Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=da644585\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F57689059&h=b8162a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180110/57689059</a>"},{"pid":"dffbdfa354620af9a1b44a267cd3b693bc051346","tid":525010,"uid":3552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1b832474779485bc5d949a515efe6e62f02f59","tid":525010,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"爽 拉晒"},{"pid":"c6f84248037567a4fe982fcf6d173ea9cb085ed6","tid":525010,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"啲老師機警咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個家長原始人黎架，隨便咬人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}